data.description: Welcome to this charming and well-maintained 2-story Georgian-style home. The main level features, a living and dining room, and kitchen with stainless steel appliances. The 2nd level has 2 nice-sized bedrooms both with closets and a full bathroom. A full basement is perfect for customization. Enjoy the privacy of a spacious and fenced backyard perfect for outdoor activities and a 2-car garage and a sliding gate for additional parking space on the concrete pad. Sold "AS-IS
